Blagoslovyena tyh v' zhenakh,<br />
Y blagoslovyen plod chreva Tvoyego,<br />
yako Spasa rodila yesi dush nashikh.</p>
</div>
</td>
<td>
<div style="font-style:italic" class="poem">
<p>Theotokos Virgin, rejoice, (or: Rejoice, O Virgin Theotokos)<br />
